data.description: What a gem in the heart of Metairie.  Downstairs is living room, den, sunroom, kitchen, dining area, laundry room, and one car garage.  Upstairs is all bedrooms with walk in closets, ceiling fans, and wooden floors plus two full bathrooms.  Primary bathroom offers vanity and garden tub (jacuzzi jets not working) while hall bath has double vanity.  Attractive crown molding throughout majority of home. Sunroom has built in bar with sitting area while looking out into the beautiful backyard.  Backyard offers a whole house generator & detached building to be used as guest quarters or storage area.  Spacious kitchen with lazy Susan; pull out draws for pantry area; gas stove; oven & microwave built into the wall; stainless steel appliances; and a lovely dining room.  Den can be a second entertaining area/playroom/office or whatever you need. Lots of storage in huge laundry room with half bath;  Keypad entry and charming front doors greet you and your guests with covered area.  Roof 2021; Flatwork June 2023; Generator May 2021; AC 2005; HWH Nov 2022; Leaf Filter April 2021; Plenty of off-street parking and only two blocks from Veterans and the parades!!!
